    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''She has served the good Lord, she has served the church, she has served us. What better legacy can she leave?''</p>
        <p>JOHN STEWART JR., on his great-aunt Emma Faust Tillman, who died at age 114. [B6]</p>
